On receipt of the surveyor's acknowledgement of the warrant, the Commissioner shall mail a notice of the issuance of the warrant to:
The applicant;
Each adjoining landowner named in the application under § 13-302(a)(4) of this subtitle;
Each person, governmental body, or agency named in the application under § 13-302(a)(6) of this subtitle as having a claim to any portion of the land described in the application;
The Division of State Documents; and
The Board of Public Works.
